  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE ISSUANCE OF STATE GENERAL OBLIGATION BONDS TO PROVIDE FUNDS TO ASSIST THE MISSISSIPPI MILITARY DEPARTMENT IN PAYING COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH PURCHASING LAND ADJACENT TO AND/OR NEAR CAMP SHELBY, AND LOCATED IN FORREST COUNTY AND PERRY COUNTY, MISSISSIPPI, FOR THE PURPOSE OF USING THE LAND FOR TRAINING AREAS AND BUFFER ZONES AT CAMP SHELBY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
